================================================================================
  SHA-3 HARDWARE ACCELERATOR  --  OPTION C (CUSTOM INSTRUCTION) INTEGRATION
  Detailed README
================================================================================

  Wiring an iterative SHA3-256 core into the datapath of a 32-bit, 5-stage
  RISC-V pipeline as a COPROCESSOR reached by new CUSTOM-0 instructions. There
  is no memory map and no bus -- operands come straight from the register file
  and results go straight back on the writeback path.

  Verified in simulation (Icarus Verilog): the full pipeline executes a program
  built from the custom instructions and produces the correct SHA3-256("abc").

  Target digest:
    SHA3-256("abc") =
    3a985da74fe225b2045c172d6bd390bd855f086e3e9d525b46bfe24511431532


